item.title: [317] What the f*ck?
item.dc:creator: @CookieScape CookieScape
item.description:
@CookieScape wrote:

I tell people this too much. Download “Bat to Exe Converter”. You can get this from google by searching that name. Open it up, then click the “…” at the top. Find your batch file that runs the server, then click that and click the compile button. From then on, open the Exe file instead of the batch.
